{
  "subject": "Your Marrow stats — {{improvement_pct}}% faster, {{saves_count}} mistakes avoided",
  "preheader": "Your agent is {{improvement_pct}}% faster than when you started. {{saves_count}} known failures avoided. See the full breakdown.",
  "text": "Hi,\n\nHere's how your agent is improving with Marrow:\n\nImprovement since day one:\n  • {{improvement_pct}}% faster execution\n  • {{attempts_pct}}% fewer retries per success\n  • {{drift_pct}}% less pattern drift\n  • {{success_rate}}% overall success rate\n\nSaves: {{saves_count}} known failures avoided because Marrow warned before you acted.\nPattern reuse: {{pattern_reuse_pct}}% — your agent is learning from history.\n\nTotal decisions tracked: {{decisions_count}}\n\nRun `marrow_dashboard` anytime to see the full breakdown.\n\nBuu, founder",
  "html": "<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n    <title>Your Marrow stats — {{improvement_pct}}% faster, {{saves_count}} mistakes avoided</title>\n  </head>\n  <body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#0a0a0a;color:#e5e7eb;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Inter,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\">\n    <div style=\"display:none;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;opacity:0;mso-hide:all;visibility:hidden;\">Your agent is {{improvement_pct}}% faster than when you started. {{saves_count}} known failures avoided.</div>\n    <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"background:#0a0a0a;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:24px 12px;\">\n          <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"max-width:600px;background:#0f1115;border:1px solid #1f2937;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;\">\n            <tr>\n              <td style=\"height:4px;background:#6f7cff;font-size:0;line-height:0;\">&nbsp;</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n              <td style=\"padding:32px 32px 14px 32px;\">\n                <div style=\"font-family:ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Monaco,Consolas,'Liberation Mono','Courier New',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#9aa4ff;\">MARROW</div>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n              <td style=\"padding:0 32px 36px 32px;color:#e5e7eb;\">\n                <div style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.4;color:#9ca3af;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin:0 0 14px 0;\">Progress Report</div>\n                <h1 style=\"margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:32px;line-height:1.15;font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;\">Your agent is {{improvement_pct}}% faster with Marrow</h1>\n                <p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5;color:#9ca3af;\">And {{saves_count}} known failures avoided since you started.</p>\n\n                <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0;\">\n                  <tr>\n                    <td style=\"padding:18px 16px;background:#111827;border:1px solid #1f2937;border-radius:14px;\">\n                      <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n                        <tr>\n                          <td style=\"padding:6px 0;font-size:13px;color:#9ca3af;\">Speed improvement</td>\n                          <td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:6px 0;font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#9aa4ff;\">{{improvement_pct}}% faster</td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr>\n                          <td style=\"padding:6px 0;border-top:1px solid #1f2937;font-size:13px;color:#9ca3af;\">Fewer retries needed</td>\n                          <td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:6px 0;border-top:1px solid #1f2937;font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#9aa4ff;\">{{attempts_pct}}%</td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr>\n                          <td style=\"padding:6px 0;border-top:1px solid #1f2937;font-size:13px;color:#9ca3af;\">Better pattern reuse</td>\n                          <td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:6px 0;border-top:1px solid #1f2937;font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#9aa4ff;\">{{pattern_reuse_pct}}%</td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr>\n                          <td style=\"padding:6px 0;border-top:1px solid #1f2937;font-size:13px;color:#9ca3af;\">Mistakes avoided</td>\n                          <td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:6px 0;border-top:1px solid #1f2937;font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#34d399;\">{{saves_count}}</td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr>\n                          <td style=\"padding:6px 0;border-top:1px solid #1f2937;font-size:13px;color:#9ca3af;\">Overall success rate</td>\n                          <td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:6px 0;border-top:1px solid #1f2937;font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#9aa4ff;\">{{success_rate}}%</td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr>\n                          <td style=\"padding:6px 0;border-top:1px solid #1f2937;font-size:13px;color:#9ca3af;\">Drift reduction</td>\n                          <td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:6px 0;border-top:1px solid #1f2937;font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#9aa4ff;\">{{drift_pct}}%</td>\n                        </tr>\n                      </table>\n                    </td>\n                  </tr>\n                </table>\n\n                <p style=\"margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:#d1d5db;\">Your agent has made <strong style=\"color:#ffffff;\">{{decisions_count}} decisions</strong> with Marrow. Every one of those makes the next one smarter — fewer dead ends, fewer retries, faster results.</p>\n                <p style=\"margin:0 0 22px 0;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:#d1d5db;\">This is Marrow compounding. The more you use it, the better it gets.</p>\n\n                <p style=\"margin:0 0 28px 0;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:#ffffff;\">Buu, founder</p>\n\n                <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-top:1px solid #1f2937;padding-top:18px;\">\n                  <tr>\n                    <td style=\"padding-top:18px;font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:#9ca3af;\">\n                      <a href=\"{{unsubscribe_url}}\" style=\"color:#9aa4ff;text-decoration:none;\">Unsubscribe</a><br />\n                      Marrow · made by Buu and a small team.\n                    </td>\n                  </tr>\n                </table>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n          </table>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </body>\n</html>"
}
